name: Cosmic Dust
description:
Cosmic dust, also called extraterrestrial dust or space dust, is dust which exists in outer space and between stars or galaxies

When I was a child I used to look at the night sky and I was always asked what the empty space between the stars really is

its from a generative art project coded via Python - Pillow
Graphed via Pytorch implementation of various GANs , using the Turtle module
Created in Adobe Photoshop 2021
